{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "本章写石破天在双凤镇与丁珰重逢。丁珰深夜潜入客店相会，情意炽烈，石破天却仍对阿绣难以忘怀，内心徘徊不定。次晨闵柔来唤，丁珰仓促藏身床底，误使石清夫妇追错方向；随后她又故意引着石破天同行，使其与父母失散。途中二人卷入关东四大门派和丁不四的冲突，丁不四武功凶悍，群豪几近覆灭。石破天在旁观战时融会所学，关键时刻出手相救，折服范一飞、高三娘子等人。众人遂邀二人同行，并在常熟设宴酬谢。不料夜间又有人上门辱及关东群豪，挑起新的约战，为后续江湖纷争埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "只听得窗上又是得得得轻击三下，这敲窗之声甚是熟悉，他心中怦的一跳，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "窗外丁珰的声音低声道：",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "想到阿绣的娇羞温雅，瞧着自己时那含情脉脉的眼色，想到她说把自己",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "，此后却再也见不到她，心下惘然若失。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "菩萨保佑，但愿你永生永世再也找不着她。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "你爷爷呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰伸手到他手臂上一扭，嗔道：",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "随即想到和阿绣同衾共枕的情景，只想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天忸怩道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰噗哧一笑，说道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "说着又叹了口气，心想：",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰却不理睬。石破天心中只想着阿绣，突然之间，明白了那日在紫烟岛树林中她瞧着自己的眼色，明白了她叫自己作",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "的含意，心中大喜若狂：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "随即又想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "叹了口气，坐到椅上，伏案竟自睡了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天应了声，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "站起身来，向丁珰望了一眼，不由得手足无措。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_rou",
      "speaker_name": "闵柔",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "你开门，我有话说！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "是我妈妈，不要紧的。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "再要跃窗而逃，其势已然不及。她本是个天不怕地不怕的姑娘，但想到要和婆婆见面，且是在如此尴尬的情景下给她撞见，不由得全身发热，眼见石破天便要拔闩开门，情急之下，右手使出",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "抓住他背心",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "，左手使",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "捏住他",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "师哥快来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_rou",
      "speaker_name": "闵柔",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "玉儿⋯⋯玉儿给人劫走啦！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "那是我爹爹妈妈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "我早知道啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰微微侧头，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "心肝宝贝",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "那怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天奇道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰哼的一声，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天心下感动，老实说出心里话：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "马蹄声响，夫妇俩牵马出店。石破天追出两步，又即停步，回头问丁珰道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "你没见过么？这般瞧我干么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "叮叮当当，你⋯⋯你真好看，比我妈妈还好看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "又想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰嘻嘻而笑，道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "当下算了房饭钱，出店而去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰抿嘴笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "看了几眼，没再理会，心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "好啊，有酒有肉，爷爷正饿得很了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "糟糕！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "别客气，大家一块儿坐！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "请，请！大家别客气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "你怎么不喝酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "这酒有些酸，不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "尊驾贵姓大名？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "你不知我姓名，本事也好不到那里去了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "那老者道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁不四笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "范一飞大怒，拍案而起，大声喝道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "这老儿莫非是长乐帮的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "长乐帮",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "当下说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "他连说三句",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "，举碗又自喝酒，脸上却笑嘻嘻地，殊无生气之状，旁人谁也不知这",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "四字意何所指。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "听他接下去连说三句",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "，便道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "原来他自己也使九节鞭。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "那虬髯汉子道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "爷爷外号叫做'一日不过四'，这里倒有一十一个贼小子使单刀，再加上这个使九节鞭的，爷爷倒要分开三日来杀⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "一日不过四",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "他⋯⋯他是丁不四！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁不四，你出来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "人不美，刀美！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "四夷宾服",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "高三娘子好飞刀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "辽东鹤小心，抓你咽喉！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天伸了伸舌头，向丁珰道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "天马行空",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "爷爷",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "小子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "怯意一去，怒气陡生，喝道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "拆到第十二招上，石破天反手抓去，使出",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "的第五变招，将金鞭鞭梢抓住。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "她叫叮叮当当，是我的⋯⋯我的⋯⋯我的⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "我的",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "咱们走罢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "是，是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "众人听了，无不哈哈大笑。丁珰也噗哧一声，笑了出来，心想：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "向丁珰道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "高三娘子这般甜嘴蜜舌的称赞，丁珰听在耳中，实是说不出的受用，抿了嘴笑了笑，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "嘤",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "高三娘子这一刀是给咱们灭烛，却叫人误会了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "那人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zheng_ping",
      "speaker_name": "吕正平",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "很好，扁脑壳在这里，你来砍罢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_san_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "高三娘子",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "去不去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "范一飞",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "不管对方是谁，既来叫了阵，咱们非得赴约不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "范一飞",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "高三娘子道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "范一飞",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "她顿了一顿，不听石破天回答，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "范一飞",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "强盗杀了人哪，救命，救命！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "范一飞",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "快去报官！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "范一飞",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "有的低声道：",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "怎么办？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "反正这里是不能住了，跟在他们后面去瞧瞧热闹罢。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "石破天",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 772,
      "line_end": 772
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "的一声，惊道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 772,
      "line_end": 772
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "丁珰道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 774
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "怎么出了个山东响马王大虎？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "那是假的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    }
  ],
